  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为工业物联网架构画一个数据流图，核心是ActuatorController如何访问TelemetryStream数据。先确定主要组件吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "CDN",
        "STORAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以起点是ActuatorController，终点是存储的TelemetryStream数据。中间需要经过DNS解析和CDN加速层吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "R53",
        "EDGE",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Route 53做DNS解析，然后到CloudFront的Edge节点。但这里有个特殊点——我们需要Lambda@Edge做边缘计算。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R53",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把DNS解析和CDN层做成两个子图，CDN内部包含Edge、Lambda、还有证书和缓存节点。先画这个结构。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DNS",
        "CDN",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "存储层也要单独一个子图，包含OAI身份和实际的文件存储。OAI这里很关键，它控制CloudFront访问S3的权限。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STORAGE",
        "OAI",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，OAI是Origin Access Identity，放在STORAGE子图里，但逻辑上它是CloudFront用来访问S3的凭证？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OAI",
        "CACHE",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "没错，所以连接关系是CACHE指向OAI，OAI再指向FILES。而且这里要标注\"OAI Only\"，表示只有OAI能直接访问存储。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CACHE",
        "OAI",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "连接画好了：USER用HTTPS到R53，R53到EDGE，EDGE到LAMBDA，LAMBDA到CERT，CERT到CACHE，CACHE标注OAI Only到OAI，最后OAI到FILES。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "R53",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE",
        "OAI",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，R53到EDGE这条线，我刚才说错了。DNS解析后返回的是CDN域名，不是直接连到EDGE节点。让我重新理一下。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R53",
        "EDGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解，但在这个架构图里，我们通常简化表示为R53指向EDGE，表示流量进入CDN边缘。需要改成别的表示方式吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R53",
        "EDGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "简化表示可以，保持这样。不过CERT的位置我需要确认——它应该在Lambda之后做证书验证，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "实际流程是：Lambda处理完请求后，如果需要回源，会经过证书验证再到缓存。所以LAMBDA到CERT再到CACHE这个顺序是合理的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "现在加上样式区分吧。ActuatorController用蓝色系，DNS用黄色，CDN用粉色，存储用绿色，这样一眼能看出层级。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "CDN",
        "STORAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "样式已应用：USER浅蓝底深蓝边，DNS浅黄底深黄边，CDN浅粉底深红边，STORAGE浅绿底深绿边。视觉效果清晰多了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "CDN",
        "STORAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "再看一眼标签命名。所有TelemetryStream相关的节点，标签都应该是IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream，ActuatorController和PLC_Logic按类型区分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R53",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "FILES",
        "USER",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE",
        "OAI"
