      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "检查完成：R53、EDGE、LAMBDA、FILES都是TelemetryStream；USER和CERT、CACHE是ActuatorController；OAI是PLC_Logic。符合工业物联网的命名规范。",
      "elements_involved": [
